# 🚀 Day 79 – Add Delete Confirmation Dialog

## 🎯 Goal

Yesterday, clicking the delete button immediately removed a report.

Today, we'll make it safer.

Instead of:

```text
🗑️ Click
      ↓
Deleted
```

We'll have:

```text
🗑️ Click
      ↓
Are you sure?
      ↓
Yes → Delete
No  → Cancel
```

This is how professional apps work.

